Name: lsof
Version: 4.89
Release: alt1

Packager: Victor Forsiuk <force@altlinux.org>

Summary: Lists files open by processes
License: Free
Group: Monitoring

URL: ftp://lsof.itap.purdue.edu/pub/tools/unix/lsof
# This is REPACKAGED upstream source, read README.lsof.maintainer!
